{"tid":1693694,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣有無人聽到啲好低沉嘅怪聲","createTime":"2019-11-04T18:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T04:28:59.000Z","uid":138740,"like":197,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8b9be8cbca79c0f899bbb2f5596cea3808a6b6","tid":1693694,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:00:03.000Z","msg":"我唔知依種聲係咪叫低頻<br />\n有啲似船駛過嘅聲，都有啲似回音嘅feel<br />\n佢係咁隔一陣就出現<br />\n我起初以為係車聲，但我聽咗一陣，<br />\n都係覺得唔係車聲，加上同時間有車間唔中駛過<br />\n完全係唔同嘅聲嚟<br />\n我嘅位置唔近海，應該無理由係船聲<br />\n如果我個位都聽到船聲，<br />\n住近海嗰啲應該會嘈到瞓唔著<br />\n我試過錄，但錄出嚟好鬼多雜聲，<br />\n根本就聽唔清楚"},{"pid":"2f5c4e09d6d11fd8acd96bf3df725c1cb7b404ee","tid":1693694,"uid":62345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"No"},{"pid":"524e0f4212464646ee2346200cbc889650796362","tid":1693694,"uid":255045,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:01:59.000Z","msg":"屯門大興個邊都有"},{"pid":"dc0df6453d78730b0367330c90014e36c51c41c0","tid":1693694,"uid":138740,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"524e0f4212464646ee2346200cbc889650796362","tid":1693694,"uid":255045,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:01:59.000Z","msg":"屯門大興個邊都有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:02:52.000Z","msg":"個聲唔係超大<br />\n又唔係超嘈<br />\n但一直聽住就勁不安"},{"pid":"bc27839fccfb1d420b13d247d06571f497bc78b7","tid":1693694,"uid":116530,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:04:05.000Z","msg":"末日號角"},{"pid":"b613b44dae09f5a40eb8b9759e10e1f9271dea02","tid":1693694,"uid":242092,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:04:43.000Z","msg":"音波炮"},{"pid":"135f81f049dafa314db419ba213919f11d8101ec","tid":1693694,"uid":160357,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:05:14.000Z","msg":"將軍澳聽過，好似好遠咁傳過嚟，好似啲號角聲咁"},{"pid":"2d60fbfd26d7503ee0f8e73248d94c4249b14bb0","tid":1693694,"uid":255045,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"quote